entries.title_d: You've been given the directive to escort the commander to Hutt Claims in the Tatoo System.
entries.title: Tatoo System: Escort the Commander
entries.thanks_3: Thanks for getting that Valarian off me!
entries.taunt_2: You'll never be successful in your launch against the Station, fools!
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast1 Hutt Informant:\#pcontrast3 < We're ready for the battle. It should be a smooth attack. Wait.. I'm getting technical readout from my scanners that there are ships with armed weapon systems in the area. We may need your help, pilot! Help us out with this battle! >
entries.reason_3: I'm ready to go. Let's get this underway.
entries.reason_2: We need teh git teh Hutt Claims teh launch our attack.
entries.reason_1: You know what to do, pilot. Escort me to Hutt Claims.
entries.quest_rendezvous_d: Meet the Commander here and guide him back to Hutt Claims safely.
entries.quest_escort_d: Escort the Commander and guide him back to Hutt Claims safely.
entries.panic_3: Pilot! I'm getting damaged! Get them off me!
entries.panic_2: Arh! Git yeh enemies off o' me.
entries.hull_half: Pilot! Pay attention! We're getting hit over here.
entries.goodbye_3: It's about time. We'll let you know when we're ready for your help.
entries.goodbye_2: Thank yeh, pilot! Yer a good seed. We're gonna set up 'ere at this point.
entries.goodbye_1: Thank you, pilot. We'll set up momentarily.
entries.found_loc: I've transmitted the information to you as to where you'll meet our war ships. Escort the commander safely and we'll begin our attack.
entries.failed_protect: Pilot! You've failed to protect our commander!
entries.failed_destroy: We've failed our directive, pilot! You could have guarded the commander better!
entries.complete: Fantastic work, pilot! Soon, we'll launch the attack from Hutt Claims and be victorious!
entries.arrived_at_loc: Stay here. The commander will arrive shortly. Always keep an eye out for Valarian influence. I feel they are near.
entries.abort: You can't abandon your mission, pilot!!
